### Your Task

**Copy the following code EXACTLY as shown below into `main.php`**

```php
<?php
// Function to greet someone
function greet($name) {
    echo "Hello, $name!\n";
}

// Function that returns a value
function add($a, $b) {
    return $a + $b;
}

// Function to calculate factorial
function factorial($n) {
    $result = 1;
    for ($i = 1; $i <= $n; $i++) {
        $result *= $i;
    }
    return $result;
}

greet("Alice");
greet("Bob");

$sum = add(5, 3);
echo "5 + 3 = $sum\n";

echo "5! = " . factorial(5) . "\n";
?>
```

